      "text": "今日の仕事はこれで終わりだが\nすずはこのまま真っ直ぐ寮に帰るのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today's work is done‚\nare you heading straight back to the dorm‚ Suzu?",
        "id": ""
      },
