      "text": "ええ、ユニットバトルに向けて\n寮で芽衣と作戦会議をする予定ですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I’m planning to have a strategy meeting\nwith Mei at the dorm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣はいつもあんな調子で世話が焼けますから\n私が率先して引っ張っていかないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei always needs to be looked after‚\nso I have to take the lead.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.2762073912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.6000000954
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "せっかく芽衣と限定ユニットを組むのですから\nやるからには優勝を目指しますわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since we’re forming a limited-time unit with Mei‚\nwe’re going to aim for victory!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
