      "text": "気合いが入っているようだな\n曲の構想はもうあるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem motivated.\nDo you have any ideas for the song yet?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
