      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "具体的な内容はこれから考えますが\n私達の好きなものを詰め込んだ曲にするつもりですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll think about the details later‚\nbut I plan to make a song that includes all the things we love.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
