      "text": "すずと芽衣の好きを詰め込んだ曲か……\nどんな感じになるのか、完成が楽しみだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A song filled with the things Suzu and Mei love…\nI’m looking forward to seeing how it turns out.",
